        <num>CCP 4363</num>
        <heading>4363.  Security instead of mortgage</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 4363.  Security instead of mortgage
Instead of the mortgage provided in Article 4362, the parent may furnish security as provided in Article 4132 or a special mortgage as provided in Article 4133.  The amount of the security or special mortgage shall be equal to the price of the adjudication.</p>
        </content>
